trans-unit.source: A persistence provider throws this exception when it expects to find an instance in the initialized state, but finds the instance is in the completed state.
trans-unit.target: 지속성 공급자는 초기화된 상태의 인스턴스를 찾을 것으로 예상했지만 완료된 상태의 인스턴스를 찾은 경우 이 예외를 throw합니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> class.
Initializes an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> class.
The reason for the exception.
Initializes an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> class using the error message.
trans-unit.target: 오류 메시지를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> 클래스의 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The information about the current exception.
The contextual information about the source or destination.
trans-unit.target: 원본 또는 대상에 대한 컨텍스트 정보입니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> class with serialized data.
trans-unit.target: serialize된 데이터를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> 클래스의 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The reason for the exception.
The exception that causes the current exception.
Initializes an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> class using the error message and the inner exception information.
trans-unit.target: 오류 메시지와 내부 예외 정보를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> 클래스의 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The XName (the combination of namespace and name) of the command.
The ID of the target instance against which the command was executed.

Initializes an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> class using the XName (the combination of namespace and name) of the command and the ID of the target instance against which the command was executed.
trans-unit.target: 명령의 XName(네임스페이스와 이름의 조합)과 명령이 실행된 대상 인스턴스의 ID를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> 클래스의 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The XName (the combination of namespace and name) of the command.
The ID of the target instance against which the command was executed.
The exception that caused the current exception.

Initializes an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> class using the XName (the combination of namespace and name) of the command, the ID of the target instance against which the command was executed, and the inner exception information passed as parameters.
trans-unit.target: 매개 변수로 전달된 내부 예외 정보, 명령의 XName(네임스페이스와 이름의 조합) 및 명령이 실행된 대상 인스턴스의 ID를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> 클래스의 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The XName (the combination of namespace and name) of the command.
The ID of the target instance against which the command was executed.
The reason for the exception.
The exception that caused the current exception.

Initializes an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> class using the XName (the combination of namespace and name) of the command, the ID of the target instance against which the command was executed, error message that explains the reason for the exception, and the exception that caused the current exception.
trans-unit.target: 명령의 XName(네임스페이스와 이름의 조합), 명령이 실행된 대상 인스턴스의 ID, 예외의 원인을 설명하는 오류 메시지, 그리고 현재 예외를 발생시킨 예외를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceCompleteException" /> 클래스의 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.
